#. type: Content of: <para>
#: blfs-en/xincludes/mozshm.xml:12
msgid ""
"If you are compiling this package in chroot you must do two things.  First, "
"as the <systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem> user, ensure that "
"<filename>/dev/shm</filename> is mounted. If you do not do this, the "
"<application>Python</application> configuration will fail with a traceback "
"report referencing "
"<filename>/usr/lib/pythonN.N/multiprocessing/synchronize.py</filename>.  "
"Run: <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Si vous compilez ce paquet dans un chroot vous devez faire deux choses.  "
"Tout d'abord, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem>, assurez-vous que "
"<filename>/dev/shm</filename> est monté. Si vous ne le faites pas, la "
"configuration de <application>Python</application> échouera avec un trace "
"évoquant "
"<filename>/usr/lib/pythonN.N/multiprocessing/synchronize.py</filename>. "
"Lancez&nbsp;: <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
